highlights.text: “אני חוזר” by מ' is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Israel, up 72 spots at #80.
Omer Adam has the most spots on Top Songs Israel. “ראיתי עולם” is the highest at #5.
“מגדלים” by STILLA and Ness is the highest new entry on Top Songs Israel at #62.
“לשוב הביתה” by Ishay Ribo has been on Top Songs Israel the longest, at 332 weeks straight.
